Package: pomodoro-lock
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-venv, python3-gi, python3-notify2, gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1
Description: Multi-display Pomodoro timer with screen overlay
 A comprehensive Pomodoro timer application that helps you maintain focus during
 work sessions and enforces breaks with full-screen overlays across all
 connected displays.
 .
 This package installs the application in userspace with a virtual environment,
 eliminating the need for system-wide Python package installation.
 .
 It runs as a user service and is designed to be compatible with
 most modern desktop environments. 